---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — JamJet"
  description="JamJet privacy policy. How we handle your data."
  canonical="https://jamjet.dev/privacy"
>

<div class="legal">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    JamJet is open-source software licensed under Apache 2.0. This privacy policy covers
    the jamjet.dev website and any hosted services operated by JamJet Labs.
  </p>

  <h2>Data we collect</h2>

  <h3>Website analytics</h3>
  <p>
    We use <a href="https://www.goatcounter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GoatCounter</a>,
    a privacy-friendly analytics tool. GoatCounter does not use cookies, does not collect
    personal data, and does not track users across sites. We collect aggregate page view
    counts and referrer information only.
  </p>

  <h3>Self-hosted runtime</h3>
  <p>
    When you run JamJet locally or on your own infrastructure, no data is sent to JamJet Labs.
    All workflow state, audit logs, and telemetry remain on your systems. The runtime does not
    phone home.
  </p>

  <h3>GitHub interactions</h3>
  <p>
    If you open issues, pull requests, or discussions on our GitHub repositories, that data is
    governed by <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub's privacy policy</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    The jamjet.dev website does not set any cookies. No first-party cookies, no third-party
    cookies, no tracking pixels.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>
    The website loads fonts from Google Fonts. Google's
    <a href="https://developers.google.com/fonts/faq/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">font privacy policy</a>
    applies to those requests.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:hello@jamjet.dev">hello@jamjet.dev</a>.
  </p>
</div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 24px 6rem;
  }
  .legal h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .legal-updated {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .legal h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .legal p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .legal a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .legal a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
